parameters: Hmm... Where on earth is this...?
Anyway, I have to investigate the situation.

I need to think of a way to communicate with the
outside...

There's a computer! We can do something with
that...

Alright! Let's connect it to my terminal... Shuu!
Shuu, can you hear me!?

Shuu! Shuu, can you hear me!? I've connected the
net to my terminal, so we should be able to locate
you by signal! Shuu!

Fuhahahaha! Are you awake, my little Resistance
puppet?
You're... President Waltin!? Then this place is...

Yes, this is the Imperial Central Presidential
Office. For you guys, it's what you'd call the
enemy's headquarters!

Ugh!? What strength, it's even stronger than the
modified soldiers from before...

How dare you ruin my auction. It was supposed to
be the highlight of my birthday...

Looking forward to human trafficking...⁉ You
really are the worst...

Hmm, well, it's fine. After all, I've managed to
get my hands on such a rare item. There's no
cyborg as powerful as this even in the empire.
Don't be ridiculous! Who would ever become yours!

Hahaha! Your audacity is commendable... but what
will you do in this situation...?

(Damn! I have to do something about the modified
soldier in front of me...!)

※There will be a choice after this. Do you want to
save? (Depending on your choice, it may result in
a game over.)
Guh...! What kind of strength is this...⁉
Hehehe... Now, what should I do...

It would be a waste to kill. I insist on making
good use of it.

...Hmm, that's right. Let's keep her alive as a
warning to the rebels...

(Calm down, Shuu should be coming to help me based
on the communication earlier... I have to buy some
time.)

I understand... So, what do you want to do? Should
I pretend to be a dog?

Hmm, that's not a bad idea, but we already have
plenty of dogs. Besides, the desire to collect is
a troublesome thing. Once you get something rare,
you want something even rarer.

Don't you understand...? I want your child, no
matter what. Aren't you curious? I wonder what we
would call a child born from a cyborg.

You're an idiot! I, as a cyborg, don't have the
ability to bear children...! No, it was taken from
me! By you people!

Fuhahahaha! My apologies! But if it's possible to
take something away, isn't it also possible to
give it back?

Creating an artificial uterus or artificial vagina
is easy with our technology. All we need to do is
modify your body to have those functions.

You... you people! What do you think people...
lives are!

Hahaha, you're quite spirited. You're supposed to
bear my child from now on, so don't get too hurt.

No good, Onee-san. You have to listen to what's
being said.

Did you forget? It's not surprising, we haven't
met for 10 years after all.
That voice... No... That can't be...
No, no, no, no, it's a lie, it's a lie...

Ahaha! It's been a while, Onee-san! We've both
changed quite a bit, haven't we?

Th-that can't be... something like this... like
this...

Onee-san! Let's live happily together under our
master! I'll forgive you for leaving me behind!
Let's work for our master! Let's kill a lot of
people for our master!

Stop... Don't say... such things to Mikoto... I'm
sorry... Let's go home together, okay...?

It's useless... She won't listen to anything other
than what I say, I've trained her that way.
You're the only one... I absolutely won't...!

Mikoto, take Esuka with you. It's time for her
modification.
